# Monorepo root ignore rules

# Node dependencies and build outputs
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/dist/
**/out/
**/build/
**/coverage/

# Sanity runtime
**/.sanity/

# Environment and secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Local tooling/state
**/.clerk/
**/.vercel/

# Logs
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# OS/editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# Keep root clean from generated archives
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
